        " اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : «مَنْ أَدَّى مَا اِفْتَرَضَ اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ فَهُوَ أَسْخَى اَلنَّاسِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1710 - The Prophet, peace be upon him and his family, said:\n\"Whoever fulfills what Allah (swt) has made obligatory upon him is the most generous of people.\""
        ]
